songs.title: Climb Out*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse 1: Ski Mask the Slump God]
... all time, yes I call her mucus
Baby know that she my slime
And if a nigga try, metal on me like a knife
Tell him, "Catch me outside"
Let my pistol outside
And if I put that Gucci on them snakes inside
Grass is greener over, and them snakes inside
[?], she like freshman, know her all your whole life
Tryna risk my case, 'cause a bitch a lil’ knife
Bitch, my name, better pop it like Sprite
Yes, I'm about to get a lose, like I'm playing Fortnite
Okay, pull up two, outside, feel like [?]
Going south for the night
Tell that bitch go

[Chorus: Ski Mask the Slump God]
This a big car, gotta climb out
Driving to the end of the fucking time now
Distorted beats, am I right now?
Flag on a plane, bitch, time out
This a big car, gotta climb out
Driving to the end of the fucking time now
Distorted beats, am I right now?
Flag on a plane, bitch, time out

[Verse 2: Austin Lam]
Come again, am I right?
Watch it spreads its wings like an angel
Driving to the night sky
Speeding towards what you pray for
Is this what you came for?
Chin up, [?]
’Til you can hear your thoughts
Drugs I don't pay for
Good thing we left him
We'll go wherever we want
